{"tid":1385613,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"識人到咗今時今日仲係會乜都旨意其他人幫佢做埋","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:05:51.000Z","uid":431,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e958122ced1db6753119487d99fdf25b3d5cd73","tid":1385613,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:23:26.000Z","msg":"有啲火滾 我諗唔止我嘅朋友 仲有唔少依類人<br />\n<br />\n不合作運動 &ndash;＞我唔想返工但唔會罷工 你哋繼續不合作啦我支持你哋<br />\n落場 &ndash;＞去唔到 我損錢當贖罪 香港加油<br />\n<br />\n我明各有各做 錢係可以買到好多物資食物<br />\n但唔單止錢一樣㗎嘛 最有力嘅支持係實體行動<br />\n多一個人多一分力 唔好乜都諗住有人幫你做埋<br />\n你搭緊車返工都可以無端端唔舒服暈<br />\n唔上前線都有大把崗位等你做 唔好再搵藉口畀自己啦"},{"pid":"d377b35d5e2610ee72d52b0c097baebe7bd45eaa","tid":1385613,"uid":221696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:24:21.000Z","msg":"裝睡的人"},{"pid":"3669c1840fea58d910c3671d1466d77a60940e6f","tid":1385613,"uid":431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d377b35d5e2610ee72d52b0c097baebe7bd45eaa","tid":1385613,"uid":221696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:24:21.000Z","msg":"裝睡的人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:25:34.000Z","msg":"勁憎佢哋口講支持攞個光環但真係乜都無做過<br />\n連叫佢airdrop文宣都話多人做唔使佢"},{"pid":"4b0325ef0de4c4556f6d0831861909c02a9179c4","tid":1385613,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:25:57.000Z","msg":"講得好岩 坐享其成"},{"pid":"b48b123056c2936176ae2e05eaa61425faff3a1d","tid":1385613,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:29:13.000Z","msg":"And u?"},{"pid":"87b300f2ae97e5155429a8ae97d4fa63b6fc5b8a","tid":1385613,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b0325ef0de4c4556f6d0831861909c02a9179c4","tid":1385613,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:25:57.000Z","msg":"講得好岩 坐享其成"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:29:36.000Z","msg":"xanb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3dc1094e5d874f24dfae496b4